        "content": "<p>Use <code>bindgen-cli</code> instead. Details in commit 08ab786556ff (\"rust: bindgen: upgrade to 0.65.1\"):</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"txt\"><pre><span></span><code>    In addition, bindgen 0.61.0 moved its CLI utility into a binary crate\n    called `bindgen-cli` [4]. Thus update the installation command in the\n    Quick Start guide.\n</code></pre></div>",
